    this class represents the requirements of a LeaderCard.

    public class representing development cards and inheriting from abstract class Card
    Discount

    Production
    public class that represents a production effect
    ResourceReqDev
    public class that represents the requirements of a DevelopmentCard
    ResourceReqLeader

    SpecialEffect
    interface containing the methods for managing the production in case of development cards and special effects in case of leader cards
    WhiteMarble
    this class represents the effect 'change the color of a white marble' of a LeaderCard
